<section id="acknowledgment">
    <form>
        <h2>Acknowledgment & Waiver</h2>
        <p>
            FOR UNFINISHED BUSINESS TO VIEW MY APPLICATION, I AGREE THAT:<br>            
            APPLYING OR BEING HIRED FOR ANY JOB DOES NOT MEAN I HAVE A CONTRACT OR THE RIGHT TO KEEP THE JOB.<br>
            NO EXISTING MATERIAL CAN CHANGE THIS.<br>
            THESE CANNOT CHANGE THE EMPLOYMENT-AT-WILL NATURE OF THE JOB.<br>
            ONLY THE PRESIDENT OR GENERAL MANAGER CAN CHANGE THIS IN WRITING.<br>
            I OR UNFINISHED BUSINESS MAY END THE JOB AT ANY TIME FOR ANY REASON.<br>
            IF HIRED, I KNOW THAT UNFINISHED BUSINESS MAY CHANGE BENEFITS, POLICIES, AND PROCEDURES, WHICH MAY REDUCE BENEFITS.<br>
            I ALLOW THE COMPANY TO CHECK ALL THE INFORMATION IN MY APPLICATION.<br>
            I KNOW THAT GIVING FALSE OR INCOMPLETE INFORMATION CAN BE A REASON FOR BEING FIRED AT ANY TIME WITH NO WARNING.<br>
            I ALLOW UNFINISHED BUSINESS TO TALK TO SCHOOLS, PREVIOUS EMPLOYERS (UNLESS I SAY OTHERWISE), REFERENCES, AND MORE.<br>
            I FREE UNFINISHED BUSINESS FROM ANY BLAME FOR DOING THESE CHECKS.
        </p>
        
        <p>
            I KNOW THAT:
        </p>
        <ol style="margin-left: 20px;">
            <li style="text-indent: -15px; padding-left: 15px;">
                UNFINISHED BUSINESS HAS A DRUG AND ALCOHOL POLICY THAT REQUIRES TESTING BEFORE AND AFTER HIRING.
            </li>
            <li style="text-indent: -15px; padding-left: 15px;">
                I MUST AGREE TO TESTING TO GET THE JOB.
            </li>
            <li style="text-indent: -15px; padding-left: 15px;">
                I HAVE TO PASS THE TESTS TO KEEP MY JOB.
            </li>
        </ol>
        
              
        <p>
            I KNOW THAT I HAVE TO PASS PHYSICAL TESTS RELATED TO THE JOB TO STAY HIRED.<br>
            I KNOW THAT UNFINISHED BUSINESS MAY ASK FOR A BACKGROUND CHECK. THIS CAN INCLUDE LOOKING AT MY CREDIT, CHARACTER, 
            REPUTATION, PERSONAL TRAITS, AND MODE OF LIVING.<br>
            IF I ASK IN WRITING, UNFINISHED BUSINESS WILL GIVE ME MORE DETAILS ABOUT THE BACKGROUND CHECK. THIS IS REQUIRED BY THE FAIR CREDIT REPORTING ACT.<br>
            I KNOW THAT I WILL BE ON PROBATION FOR 60 DAYS.<br>
            I CAN BE FIRED FOR ANY REASON DURING OR AFTER THIS TIME.
        </p>
        
        <p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <label for="agreement">By clicking, I agree to the above</label>
